Here's the complete list of API endpoints in the application:

## **Invoice Endpoints**

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| POST | `/api/invoices/save` | Save a new invoice |
| POST | `/api/invoices/submit` | Submit invoice to MRA |
| GET | `/api/invoices/pending` | Get all pending invoices |
| GET | `/api/invoices/processed` | Get processed invoices |
| GET | `/api/invoices/:id` | Get invoice by ID |
| DELETE | `/api/invoices/:id` | Delete invoice |
| POST | `/api/invoices/process-pending` | Manually trigger processor |
| GET | `/api/invoices/submissions` | Get submission history with ValidationURL |
| GET | `/api/invoices/failed` | Get failed submissions |
| GET | `/api/invoices/processing-history/:id` | Get processing history |
| GET | `/api/invoices/stats` | Get invoice statistics |
| GET | `/api/invoices/submission-history` | Get all submission history |
| GET | `/api/invoices/submission-stats` | Get submission statistics |

## **Demo Invoice Endpoints (Sage Simulation)**

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| POST | `/api/demo-invoices` | Create demo invoice |
| GET | `/api/demo-invoices` | List all demo invoices |

## **Inventory Endpoints**

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| POST | `/api/inventory/save` | Save inventory item |
| POST | `/api/inventory/upload` | Upload inventory to MRA |
| GET | `/api/inventory/pending` | Get pending inventory |
| GET | `/api/inventory/submitted` | Get submitted inventory |
| GET | `/api/inventory/:id` | Get inventory by ID |
| DELETE | `/api/inventory/:id` | Delete inventory |
| GET | `/api/inventory/check-barcode` | Check if barcode exists |
| POST | `/api/inventory/seed-demo` | Seed demo products |
| GET | `/api/inventory/failed` | Get failed submissions |
| POST | `/api/inventory/process-pending` | Manually trigger processor |
| GET | `/api/inventory/stats` | Get inventory statistics |

## **Terminal Endpoints**

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| POST | `/api/terminal/activate` | Activate terminal |
| GET | `/api/terminal/status` | Get terminal status |
| GET | `/api/terminal/details` | Get terminal details |
| GET | `/api/terminal/history` | Get activation history |
| POST | `/api/terminal/reset` | Reset terminal |

## **Reports Endpoints**

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| GET | `/api/reports/invoices` | Get invoice report |
| GET | `/api/reports/inventory` | Get inventory report |
| GET | `/api/reports/summary` | Get summary statistics |
| GET | `/api/reports/failed-invoices` | Get failed invoices |
| GET | `/api/reports/failed-inventory` | Get failed inventory |
| POST | `/api/reports/retry-invoice/:id` | Retry failed invoice |
| GET | `/api/reports/all-submissions` | Get all submissions |
| GET | `/api/reports/debug` | Debug database |

## **Utility Endpoints**

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| GET | `/api/utils/vat-info` | Get VAT information |
| POST | `/api/utils/calculate-vat` | Calculate VAT |
| POST | `/api/utils/validate-vat` | Validate VAT number |

## **Health Check**

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| GET | `/health` | Health check endpoint |